"<classname>TreeModelColumn</classname> del cual genera un widget "
"<classname>Gtk::View::Column</classname> apropiado."

#: C/gtkmm-tutorial-in.xml:2503(para)
msgid ""
"Here is some example code from <filename>gtkmm/demos/gtk-demo/"
